- title "Change plan"

%p
  You are currently on the <strong class="highlight">#{Plan.find(current_user.plan).name}</strong> plan and can play for <strong class="highlight">#{current_user.total_credits.minutes / 1.hour}</strong> hours each month.

#plans
  %table
    %thead
      %tr.name
        %th.free Free
        %th.casual Casual
        %th.hardcore Hardcore
        %th.pro Pro
    %tbody
      %tr.price
        %td.free Free
        %td.casual $3.95 / mo
        %td.hardcore $7.95 / mo
        %td.pro $11.95 / mo
      %tr.hours
        %td.free 4 hrs / mo
        %td.casual 40 hrs / mo
        %td.hardcore 80 hrs / mo
        %td.pro 160 hrs / mo
      %tr.worlds
        %td.free 1 world
        %td.casual 5 worlds
        %td.hardcore 10 worlds
        %td.pro 40 worlds
      %tr.buy
        - Plan.all.each do |plan|
          %td
            - if current_user.plan != plan.stripe_id
              %a{href: new_order_path(plan: plan.stripe_id)}= plan_change_action current_user, plan
            - else
              \-

- after do
  %p You can change plans at any time. Any changes in your plan will be pro-rated until your next billing cycle.